&lt;Domtar Inc> said it plans atwo-for-one stock split to take effect May 14.    The company said shareholders will be asked to approve thesplit at the annual meeting on April 29.    Domtar said its directors believe the split could favorablyaffect marketability of the shares and encourage widerdistribution.    The shares have been trading recently in a range of 45dlrs. Domtar stock was previously split on a two-for-one basisin June, 1985. Reuter&#3;